title: Drakeo The Ruler’s First Interview Out of Prison
description:
Drakeo is finally out! First thing he did was going to the studio, second thing, doing his first interview with Adam where he talks about how it feels to be a free man, the very little support he received while locked up, rappers bitting his style, his upcoming music and more!
